隨著時間的推移，區域經濟整合會逐漸產生那些動態效果？請列舉四
種可能的動態效果並說明之。（10 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:25:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "49f91d94d33d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114140", "c": "104", "s": "1105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "國際經濟", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "diplomatic", "civil_category": "外交領事人員-越南文組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('diplomatic-36ccc47a-moex-00013', 'diplomatic-36ccc47a', 'diplomatic-36ccc47a-moex-114-e6f33b51', 'sub-diplomatic-36ccc47a-02', NULL, 'essay', '根據彈性方法（elasticityapproach）與支用方法（absorptionapproach）的
